This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image reconstruction using CT technology. It also involves high-performance computing, which suggests it could belong to the Distributed Computing (cs.DC) category. The use of GPUs and parallel computing also suggests it could belong to the Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) category. The use of MPI collective communication steps suggests it could belong to the Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed) category. Finally, the use of supercomputers suggests it could belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) category.
